// Meta Relation Test Suite
// SongLang 메타 관계 시스템 테스트

// ============================================
// Part 1: 역관계 (Inverse Relation)
// ============================================

// OWNS 관계 정의 (역관계 포함)
OWNS IS RELATION
OWNS HAS Owner (Node)
OWNS HAS Item (Node)
OWNS HAS INVERSE OWNED_BY

OWNS DO
    Owner HAS Inventory Item
END

// 엔티티 생성
Player IS Entity
Player HAS Name "Hero"

Sword IS Weapon
Sword HAS Name "Excalibur"
Sword HAS Damage 50

Shield IS Weapon
Shield HAS Name "Dragon Shield"
Shield HAS Defense 30

// 관계 실행
Player OWNS Sword
Player OWNS Shield

// 쿼리 테스트: Player가 소유한 것들
Player OWNS ?

// 쿼리 테스트: Sword를 소유한 것
? OWNS Sword

// ============================================
// Part 2: 양방향 관계 (Bidirectional)
// ============================================

KNOWS IS RELATION
KNOWS HAS Person1 (Node)
KNOWS HAS Person2 (Node)
KNOWS HAS DIRECTION BIDIRECTIONAL

Alice IS Person
Alice HAS Name "Alice"

Bob IS Person
Bob HAS Name "Bob"

Alice KNOWS Bob

// 양쪽 모두 쿼리 가능해야 함
Alice KNOWS ?
Bob KNOWS ?

// ============================================
// Part 3: 전체 관계 쿼리
// ============================================

// 모든 OWNS 관계 조회
? OWNS ?

// Player의 모든 관계 조회
Player HAS ?

